                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 23,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Venti_icon.png",
                      "name": "Venti",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "This weapon's special effect will trigger before Venti unleashes an Elemental Skill, allowing him to continuously receive a boost from this weapon's special effect with each Elemental Skill. Since Venti's Elemental Burst is a snapshot skill, he can reliably gain this buff, which makes this weapon a backup choice to The Stringless.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2265,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/22/35428890/497dd6fac3d3c652a367c67428550747_306268558608889633.png",
                      "name": "Tighnari",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "This weapon increases Elemental Mastery, which increases the buffs from Tighnari's talents. After using an Elemental Skill, it increases ATK for a short duration, which makes it suitable for quick swap builds.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "name": "Fischl",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Due to the snapshot mechanic, Oz will constantly receive the buff from this weapon's special effect while using Elemental Skills. Once Oz unleashes an Elemental Burst, press E to summon and receive the buff from this weapon's special effect. This weapon is an ideal choice for Fischl off-field without The Stringless.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2268,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/24/194600931/37a18b6b6865c59063003a9380f08225_7758071773430345954.png",
                      "name": "Collei",
